# No-AI Use Rider

## Scope
This rider applies to all code and content in this repository unless otherwise noted.
The base license is the MIT License (see LICENSE).

## Additional Terms
In addition to the terms of the MIT License:

1. You may **not** use this repository, in whole or in part, including its source code or derivatives, to train, fine-tune, or otherwise improve any  machine learning or artificial-intelligence system.
2. You may **not** include this repository or its contents in any dataset or corpus used for AI/ML training.
3. You may **not** provide automated access to this repository or its contents for the purpose of AI/ML training.

These restrictions apply to both commercial and non-commercial uses.

Alternative licensing terms may be available directly from the author.

